# Agent autonomy (pre-authorized)

Human authorized **automatic execution** for agents and subagents on this repo without repeated permission prompts.

## Allowed without asking

- Local verify: pytest, flake8, alembic, poetry check
- Git: status, diff, commit, push `origin master` for ship work
- VPS: `scripts/vps_deploy.py`, `scripts/vps_configure_neon.py` (env secrets only)
- CI: `gh run list`, GitHub API, ci-watcher subagent
- `docs/implementation-notes.md` updates (no secrets)

## Still ask or block

- Force push, delete files, mass replace, CI/hooks skip — only with explicit human message
- Never commit `.env` or credentials

Policy detail: `.cursor/permissions.json` (Auto-review classifier).
